public class All_153
{
    public static void main(String args[]){
        for( int a=1; a<=9; a++ )
            for( int b=0; b<=9; b++ )
                for( int c=0; c<=9; c++ )
                    if( a*a*a+b*b*b+c*c*c == 100*a+10*b+c)
                        System.out.println( 100*a+10*b+c );
                        /**
                         * 153
                         * 370
                         * 371
                         * 407
                         */
    }
}
第二个例子 
class All_628
{
    public static void main( String[] args){
        for( int n=1; n<=9999; n++)
            if( n==divsum(n)  ) System.out.println(n);
            /**
             * 6
             * 28
             * 496
             * 8128
             */
    }
    public static int divsum( int n ){
        int s = 0;
        for( int i=1; i<n; i++ )
            if( n%i == 0 ) s+=i;
        return s;
    }
}
第三个例子 
class All_220
{
    public static void main( String[] args){
        for( int n=1; n<=9999; n++){
            int s = divsum(n);
            if( n>s && divsum(s)==n )
                System.out.println(n +"," + s);
                /**
                 * 284,220
                 * 1210,1184
                 * 2924,2620
                 * 5564,5020
                 * 6368,6232
                 */
        }
    }
    public static int divsum( int n ){
        int s = 0;
        for( int i=1; i<n; i++ )
            if( n%i == 0 ) s+=i;
        return s;
    }
}

public class Sqrt
{
    public static void main(String args[]){
        System.out.println( sqrt( 98.0 ) ); // 9.899494936718176
        System.out.println( Math.sqrt(98.0) ); // 9.899494936611665
    }

    static double sqrt( double a ){
        double x=1.0;
        do{
            x = ( x + a/x ) /2;
            System.out.println( x + "," + a/x );
            /**
             * 49.5,1.97979797979798
             * 25.73989898989899,3.8073187481605024
             * 14.773608869029745,6.633450287521802
             * 10.703529578275774,9.15585828798978
             * 9.929693933132777,9.869387783746262
             * 9.899540858439519,9.899449014996833
             * 9.899494936718176,9.899494936505155
             */
        }while( Math.abs(x*x-a)/a > 1e-6 );
        return x;
    }
}
